episodes.title: The Cult That Inspired Manson
episodes.description:
This is the story of Krishna Venta and his forgotten WKFL Fountain of the World cult. Before Charles Manson would make the Santa Susana Pass his group’s home, this cult occupied a compound only a few miles away, with strangely similar beliefs. Some Manson members would even stay with this cult before moving to Spahn Ranch. Join me as I dive into the history of this strange cult.
